Put your best Santa_Hat on and start your Christmas celebrations with some exercise . Join our annual Xmas_Joy Ride around your favourite district . Own the night by bringing a light , helmet and hi - vis gear on top of your best Santa outfit . Prizes for Best_Dressed will apply !
Afterwards we will gather for a Christmas drink at Container_Pub on Street 15 in An_Phu ( just behind the Vista ) - ALL welcome to this . For safety reasons children under 12 are not permitted on the ride .
